 scope Logflare operations.</td></tr><tr><td><code>LOGFLARE_LOG_LEVEL</code=
></td><td>String, defaults to <code>info</code>. <br>Options: <code>error</=
code>,<code>warning</code>, <code>info</code></td><td>Allows runtime config=
uration of log level.</td></tr><tr><td><code>LOGFLARE_NODE_HOST</code></td>=
<td>string, defaults to <code>127.0.0.1</code></td><td>Sets node host on st=
